Help prepare and participate in presentations to client senior leadership and senior management roles to help educate and inform them and to gain their consensus.

Must be a U.S. Citizen with the ability to obtain/maintain a government security clearance if required.
3-5 years in the role of business analyst performing most if not all of the above job responsibilities;
